7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Cohere and HuggingChat share a solid foundation of core features including Web Search, Multilingual. Where Cohere pulls ahead is with exclusive access to File Upload and Api Access and Citations, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Cohere holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10, while HuggingChat scores 5/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Cohere and HuggingChat offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Cohere's free tier and HuggingChat's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
